Hey! This is my first map, so I'd like to explain it!

POWER is a sort of map I made for CS:S (because I fail and can't make a mod).

POWER maps focus on two sides making it to one focal point that connects both sides, giving either team the advantage. The focus of POWER maps is to use the different classes as a team to "take" the focal point and have the advantage over the other team.
There are four "classes" in POWER maps:
3 Technicians - They have machine guns and are decent overall. They are used for backing up other players and leading assaults.
3 Snipers - They have sniper rifles and excel in range. They are used for taking out enemies from a distance.
3 Guards - They have pump shotguns and excel in damage. They are used for guarding the focal point of the map and assisting in assaults.
1 Special Ops - They have a silenced sub-machine gun and excel in stealth. Their uses are varied.

...umm...yeah. Sorry for it sounding stupid, but give it a try! ^_^;

A map designed for 1v1 wars, but also up to 5v5 or 6v6 (Max 10x10). The map contains different rooms, rooms for different types of combat.

# 4 rooms
- First room is the spawn room, which contains the portals to the other rooms.
- There is an 'Assualt Room' where there you will battle with AK's, M4's and MP5's.
- The theme is some sort of dumping ground, or demolished site.
- There is a 'Sniper Room' where you will battle it out with AWP's in an underground cave with a stream.
- There is a 'Knife' Room for you to battle your mates at 1v1 or 10v10 knife wars, the theme is a messy kitchen.

# Features
- There are 3 portals for the 3 battle rooms for each team. The room that you spawn in you can see the enemy but cannot shoot them through the bullet-proof glass which separates you.
- There are return portals for each room, so you can return to the main portal room and choose another room to go too.
- There are several secret ladders, and hidden weapons for you to find.

Please Leave your comments, they will be much appreciated
Enjoy

Here is a fully playable 1 player mini-game version of the Plants vs. Zombies indie game. The concept of the map is simple; gather sun, plant plants and stop the zombies from eating your brain!

Features of the map;

- 7 Levels of zombies, were each level spawns dozens of zombies

- 6 Types of zombies, including zombies armed with car doors

- 6 Different custom plant models

- 2 Versions of the garden

- Easy and Hard difficulty

- Awesome PvZ music

- Information buttons everywhere for the beginners

Majority of the credits goes to Charli, since he is the major creator of the advanced triggers, functions and outputs that made this map functional.

Please enjoy,
Charli and Lickwim.

Note: If you are familiar with the PvZ concept, you should start playing at the hard difficulty. Also, if you find your radar missing after playing this map, simply type cl_radaralpha 255 in the console. :)
